         MACRO
         BBOACGAA  ,
*
* The following control block (BBOACGAA) is used in
* bboatrue.cicsasm.
*
* Note: keep the assembler and plx mapping in sync
*
* We get a 4096 byte area for this - so we can grow this if needed.
*
BBOACGAA DSECT                       Global Work Area for BBOATRUE
BBOACGAA_EYE     DS CL8         0x00 Eyecatcher BBOACGAA
BBOACGAA_VER     DS H           0x08 Version
BBOACGAA_SIZ     DS H           0x0A Size
BBOACGAA_FLAGS   DS F           0x0C Flags
BBOACGAA_PCNUM_TWAS DS F        0x10 PC # to use for calling tWAS PC1
BBOACGAA_TRACELVL DS F          0x14 Trace level to send to PC routine
BBOACGAA_TRACELVLX DS F         0x18 Trace on|off 0|1 for BBOATRUE
BBOACGAA_CTL_TRAN DS CL4        0x1C Name of BBOACNTL transaction
          MEND                  0x20 Length of CGAA
